<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>전일 시장 요약</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f3f5f8;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --line: #e6e9ee;
      --line-strong: #cfd6df;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --up: #d14b45;
      --down: #2f7dbd;
      --shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.06);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fafc 0%, #f3f5f8 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid #edf1f5;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      padding: 24px;
    }

    h1 { font-size: 38px; margin: 0; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
    .meta { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); }

    .grid { margin-top: 18px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 16px; }

    .section { border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; background: #fff; }
    .section h2 { margin: 0; padding: 12px 14px; font-size: 21px; font-weight: 800; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); background: #fafbfd; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }

    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; border-top: 2px solid var(--line-strong); }
    td { border: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: center; padding: 10px 8px; vertical-align: middle; }

    .name { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #374151; background: #fbfcfd; line-height: 1.2; word-break: keep-all; }

    .value { padding: 8px 6px; }
    .value-inner {
      min-height: 62px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 3px;
      overflow: hidden;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }

    .price {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      white-space: nowrap;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .change {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 4px;
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 19px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .cols-3 .price { font-size: clamp(19px, 2.2vw, 28px); }
    .cols-3 .change { font-size: clamp(12px, 1.4vw, 16px); }

    .arrow { font-size: 0.85em; }
    .up { color: var(--up); }
    .down { color: var(--down); }
    .flat { color: #8b95a1; }

    .full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .commodity .name { width: 32%; }
    .commodity .value { width: 68%; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      body { padding: 14px; }
      .wrap { padding: 14px; border-radius: 12px; }
      h1 { font-size: 30px; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; }
      .section h2 { font-size: 19px; }
      .name { font-size: 16px; }
      .value-inner { min-height: 56px; }
      .price { font-size: 24px; }
      .cols-3 .price { font-size: 20px; }
      .change { font-size: 14px; }
      .cols-3 .change { font-size: 13px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>전일 시장 요약</h1>
    <div class="meta">기준일 {{ report_date }} · 생성시각 {{ generated_at }}</div>
    <div class="meta">검증 PASS 기준: NAVER 대비 종가 오차율 {{ "%.2f"|format(validation_tolerance_pct) }}% 이하</div>

    <div class="grid">
      <section class="section"><h2>국내</h2><table class="cols-2"><tr>{% for item in kr_indices[:2] %}<td class="name">{{ item.name_ko }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr><tr>{% for item in kr_indices[:2] %}{% include 'value_cell.j2' %}{% endfor %}</tr></table></section>

      <section class="section"><h2>환율</h2><table class="cols-2"><tr>{% for item in fx[:2] %}<td class="name">{{ item.name_ko }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr><tr>{% for item in fx[:2] %}{% include 'value_cell.j2' %}{% endfor %}</tr></table></section>

      <section class="section"><h2>미국</h2><table class="cols-3"><tr>{% for item in us_indices[:3] %}<td class="name">{{ item.name_ko }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr><tr>{% for item in us_indices[:3] %}{% include 'value_cell.j2' %}{% endfor %}</tr></table></section>

      <section class="section"><h2>해외(아시아)</h2><table class="cols-2"><tr>{% for item in asia_indices[:2] %}<td class="name">{{ item.name_ko }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr><tr>{% for item in asia_indices[:2] %}{% include 'value_cell.j2' %}{% endfor %}</tr></table></section>

      <section class="section commodity full"><h2>상품</h2><table class="cols-2">{% for item in commodities %}<tr><td class="name">{{ item.name_ko }}</td>{% include 'value_cell.j2' %}</tr>{% endfor %}</table></section>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
